      "text": [
        "637 - وَقَالَ أَبُو اَلْحَسَنِ اَلرِّضَا عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ: «اَلصَّلاَةُ قُرْبَانُ كُلِّ تَقِيٍّ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.637 - Abu Al-Hasan, Imam Ali ibn Musa Ar-Ridha (as), said:\n\"Prayer is the means of nearness for every pious person.\""
        ]
      }
    }
